-------

RooCMSShape::bkgPass[ x=x alpha=acmsP beta=betaP gamma=gammaP peak=peakP ] = 1.91031

variables
---------
(acmsF,acmsP,alphaF,alphaP,betaF,betaP,eff,gammaF,gammaP,meanF,meanP,nBkgF,nBkgP,nF,nP,nSigF,nSigP,peakF,peakP,sigmaF,sigmaF_2,sigmaP,sigmaP_2,sosF,sosP,x)

p.d.f.s
-------
RooCMSShape::bkgFail[ x=x alpha=acmsF beta=betaF gamma=gammaF peak=peakF ] = 1.91031

variables
---------
(acmsF,acmsP,alphaF,alphaP,betaF,betaP,eff,gammaF,gammaP,meanF,meanP,nBkgF,nBkgP,nF,nP,nSigF,nSigP,peakF,peakP,sigmaF,sigmaF_2,sigmaP,sigmaP_2,sosF,sosP,x)

p.d.f.s
-------
RooCMSShape::bkgFail[ x=x alpha=acmsF beta=betaF gamma=gammaF peak=peakF ] = 1.91031
RooCMSShape::bkgPass[ x=x alpha=acmsP beta=betaP gamma=gammaP peak=peakP ] = 1.91031

variables
---------

variables
---------
(acmsF,acmsP,alphaF,alphaP,betaF,betaP,eff,gammaF,gammaP,meanF,meanP,nBkgF,nBkgP,nF,nP,nSigF,nSigP,peakF,peakP,sigmaF,sigmaF_2,sigmaP,sigmaP_2,sosF,sosP,x)

variables

(acmsF,acmsP,alphaF,alphaP,betaF,betaP,eff,gammaF,gammaP,meanF,meanP,nBkgF,nBkgP,nF,nP,nSigF,nSigP,peakF,peakP,sigmaF,sigmaF_2,sigmaP,sigmaP_2,sosF,sosP,x)

p.d.f.s
-------
RooCMSShape::bkgFail[ x=x alpha=acmsF beta=betaF gamma=gammaF peak=peakF ] = 1.91031
RooCMSShape::bkgPass[ x=x alpha=acmsP beta=betaP gamma=gammaP peak=peakP ] = 1.91031
RooAddPdf::pdfFail[ nSigF * sigFail + nBkgF * bkgFail ] = 16.49
RooAddPdf::pdfPass[ nSigP * sigPass + nBkgP * bkgPass ] = 18.6011
RooFFTConvPdf::sigFail[ sigPhysFail(x) (*) sigResFail(x) ] = 0.105861
RooFFTConvPdf::sigPass[ sigPhysPass(x) (*) sigResPass(x) ] = 0.119509
RooHistPdf::sigPhysFail[ pdfObs=(x) ] = 35600
RooHistPdf::sigPhysPass[ pdfObs=(x) ] = 35600
RooCBExGaussShape::sigResFail[ m=x  m0=meanF  sigma=sigResFail_3  alpha=alphaF  n=nF  sigma_2=sigResFail_6 ] = 0.0017463
RooCBExGaussShape::sigResPass[ m=x  m0=meanP  sigma=sigResPass_3  alpha=alphaP  n=nP  sigma_2=sigResPass_6 ] = 0.00139743

functions
--------
RooFormulaVar::sigResFail_3[ actualVars=(sigmaF,sosF) formula="sqrt(sigmaF*sigmaF+sosF*sosF)" ] = 2.23607
RooFormulaVar::sigResFail_6[ actualVars=(sigmaF_2,sosF) formula="sqrt(sigmaF_2*sigmaF_2+sosF*sosF)" ] = 2.23607
RooFormulaVar::sigResPass_3[ actualVars=(sigmaP,sosP) formula="sqrt(sigmaP*sigmaP+sosP*sosP)" ] = 1.41421
RooFormulaVar::sigResPass_6[ actualVars=(sigmaP_2,sosP) formula="sqrt(sigmaP_2*sigmaP_2+sosP*sosP)" ] = 1.80278

variables
---------
(acmsF,acmsP,alphaF,alphaP,betaF,betaP,eff,gammaF,gammaP,meanF,meanP,nBkgF,nBkgP,nF,nP,nSigF,nSigP,peakF,peakP,sigmaF,sigmaF_2,sigmaP,sigmaP_2,sosF,sosP,x)

p.d.f.s
-------
RooCMSShape::bkgFail[ x=x alpha=acmsF beta=betaF gamma=gammaF peak=peakF ] = 1.91031
RooCMSShape::bkgPass[ x=x alpha=acmsP beta=betaP gamma=gammaP peak=peakP ] = 1.91031

variables
---------
(acmsF,acmsP,alphaF,alphaP,betaF,betaP,eff,gammaF,gammaP,meanF,meanP,nBkgF,nBkgP,nF,nP,nSigF,nSigP,peakF,peakP,sigmaF,sigmaF_2,sigmaP,sigmaP_2,sosF,sosP,x)

p.d.f.s
-------
RooCMSShape::bkgFail[ x=x alpha=acmsF beta=betaF gamma=gammaF peak=peakF ] = 1.91031
RooCMSShape::bkgPass[ x=x alpha=acmsP beta=betaP gamma=gammaP peak=peakP ] = 1.91031
RooAddPdf::pdfFail[ nSigF * sigFail + nBkgF * bkgFail ] = 16.49
RooAddPdf::pdfPass[ nSigP * sigPass + nBkgP * bkgPass ] = 18.6011
RooFFTConvPdf::sigFail[ sigPhysFail(x) (*) sigResFail(x) ] = 0.105861
RooFFTConvPdf::sigPass[ sigPhysPass(x) (*) sigResPass(x) ] = 0.119509
RooHistPdf::sigPhysFail[ pdfObs=(x) ] = 35600
RooHistPdf::sigPhysPass[ pdfObs=(x) ] = 35600
RooCBExGaussShape::sigResFail[ m=x  m0=meanF  sigma=sigResFail_3  alpha=alphaF  n=nF  sigma_2=sigResFail_6 ] = 0.0017463
RooCBExGaussShape::sigResPass[ m=x  m0=meanP  sigma=sigResPass_3  alpha=alphaP  n=nP  sigma_2=sigResPass_6 ] = 0.00139743

functions
--------
RooFormulaVar::sigResFail_3[ actualVars=(sigmaF,sosF) formula="sqrt(sigmaF*sigmaF+sosF*sosF)" ] = 2.23607
RooFormulaVar::sigResFail_6[ actualVars=(sigmaF_2,sosF) formula="sqrt(sigmaF_2*sigmaF_2+sosF*sosF)" ] = 2.23607
RooFormulaVar::sigResPass_3[ actualVars=(sigmaP,sosP) formula="sqrt(sigmaP*sigmaP+sosP*sosP)" ] = 1.41421
RooFormulaVar::sigResPass_6[ actualVars=(sigmaP_2,sosP) formula="sqrt(sigmaP_2*sigmaP_2+sosP*sosP)" ] = 1.80278

--------

variables
---------
(acmsF,acmsP,alphaF,alphaP,betaF,betaP,eff,gammaF,gammaP,meanF,meanP,nBkgF,nBkgP,nF,nP,nSigF,nSigP,peakF,peakP,sigmaF,sigmaF_2,sigmaP,sigmaP_2,sosF,sosP,x)

p.d.f.s
-------
RooCMSShape::bkgFail[ x=x alpha=acmsF beta=betaF gamma=gammaF peak=peakF ] = 1.91031
RooCMSShape::bkgPass[ x=x alpha=acmsP beta=betaP gamma=gammaP peak=peakP ] = 1.91031
RooAddPdf::pdfFail[ nSigF * sigFail + nBkgF * bkgFail ] = 16.49
RooAddPdf::pdfPass[ nSigP * sigPass + nBkgP * bkgPass ] = 18.6011
RooFFTConvPdf::sigFail[ sigPhysFail(x) (*) sigResFail(x) ] = 0.105861
RooFFTConvPdf::sigPass[ sigPhysPass(x) (*) sigResPass(x) ] = 0.119509
RooHistPdf::sigPhysFail[ pdfObs=(x) ] = 35600
RooHistPdf::sigPhysPass[ pdfObs=(x) ] = 35600
RooCBExGaussShape::sigResFail[ m=x  m0=meanF  sigma=sigResFail_3  alpha=alphaF  n=nF  sigma_2=sigResFail_6 ] = 0.0017463
RooCBExGaussShape::sigResPass[ m=x  m0=meanP  sigma=sigResPass_3  alpha=alphaP  n=nP  sigma_2=sigResPass_6 ] = 0.00139743

functions
--------
RooFormulaVar::sigResFail_3[ actualVars=(sigmaF,sosF) formula="sqrt(sigmaF*sigmaF+sosF*sosF)" ] = 2.23607
RooFormulaVar::sigResFail_6[ actualVars=(sigmaF_2,sosF) formula="sqrt(sigmaF_2*sigmaF_2+sosF*sosF)" ] = 2.23607
RooFormulaVar::sigResPass_3[ actualVars=(sigmaP,sosP) formula="sqrt(sigmaP*sigmaP+sosP*sosP)" ] = 1.41421
RooFormulaVar::sigResPass_6[ actualVars=(sigmaP_2,sosP) formula="sqrt(sigmaP_2*sigmaP_2+sosP*sosP)" ] = 1.80278

---------

-------
RooCMSShape::bkgFail[ x=x alpha=acmsF beta=betaF gamma=gammaF peak=peakF ] = 1.91031
RooCMSShape::bkgPass[ x=x alpha=acmsP beta=betaP gamma=gammaP peak=peakP ] = 1.91031
RooAddPdf::pdfFail[ nSigF * sigFail + nBkgF * bkgFail ] = 16.49
RooAddPdf::pdfPass[ nSigP * sigPass + nBkgP * bkgPass ] = 18.6011

functions
--------
RooFormulaVar::sigResFail_3[ actualVars=(sigmaF,sosF) formula="sqrt(sigmaF*sigmaF+sosF*sosF)" ] = 2.23607
RooFormulaVar::sigResFail_6[ actualVars=(sigmaF_2,sosF) formula="sqrt(sigmaF_2*sigmaF_2+sosF*sosF)" ] = 2.23607

functions
--------
RooFormulaVar::sigResFail_3[ actualVars=(sigmaF,sosF) formula="sqrt(sigmaF*sigmaF+sosF*sosF)" ] = 2.23607
RooFormulaVar::sigResFail_6[ actualVars=(sigmaF_2,sosF) formula="sqrt(sigmaF_2*sigmaF_2+sosF*sosF)" ] = 2.23607
RooFormulaVar::sigResPass_3[ actualVars=(sigmaP,sosP) formula="sqrt(sigmaP*sigmaP+sosP*sosP)" ] = 1.41421
RooFormulaVar::sigResPass_6[ actualVars=(sigmaP_2,sosP) formula="sqrt(sigmaP_2*sigmaP_2+sosP*sosP)" ] = 1.80278
